      • getTerms

        public java.util.HashSet<java.lang.String> getTerms()
        Get all the constants. If it's a word variable save just the content and remove the asterisk suffix. If it's a token, remove the token number suffix. For use in pruning application rules, this routine assumes that procedures and sumo clauses are not considered.

        public java.util.HashSet<CNF.Subst> unifyRecurse(Clause c,
                                                 CNF cnf)

      • unifyRecurse

        public java.util.HashSet<CNF.Subst> unifyRecurse(CNF cnf)
        Iterate through all possibilities of applying a given clause from the "rule" to the "content", then recurse on applying the remaining clauses. Note that every clause in this must unify consistently with some clause in cnf or the routine will return null.
